" , it will replace W in command line with w, but only if it is neither
" followed nor preceded by word character, so :W<CR> will be replaced with
" :w<CR>, but :Write won't.
cnoreabbrev W w
cnoreabbrev Q q
cnoreabbrev Wq wq
cnoreabbrev WQ wq

